{
  "texts": [
    "It introduces a \"question bank exam\" mode.",
    "MMLU (Hendrycks et al, 2021b) assesses subjects ranging from traditional fields like mathematics and history to professional areas such as law and ethics, covering 57 subjects with difficulty levels from elementary to professional.",
    "As the content of MMLU is in English, CMMLU (Li et al, 2023d) is created as its Chinese counterpart for evaluating subject knowledge proficiency in a Chinese context, covering 67 subjects.",
    "M3KE (Liu et al, 2023a), originating from the Chinese education system, collects multiple-choice questions from 71 subjects spanning from primary school to university.",
    "XiezhiBenchmark (Gu et al, 2023), covering a record 516 different subjects, attains a scale of approximately 250K questions."
  ]
}